assertion_line: 43
expression: "get_subcommand_help(\"sandbox\")"
---
Apply sandbox restrictions and exec commands

Usage: sandbox <COMMAND>

Commands:
  exec         Apply sandbox restrictions and exec a command
  test         Test sandbox enforcement interactively
  check        Check if sandboxing is supported on this platform
  create       Create a new named sandbox profile
  delete       Delete a named sandbox profile
  list         List all named sandbox profiles
  add-rule     Add a filesystem rule to a named sandbox
  remove-rule  Remove a filesystem rule from a named sandbox by path
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
